HEADWORD: Demiss
<hw>De*miss"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>demissus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>demittere</ets>.]</ety> <def>Cast
down; humble; submissive.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He down descended like a most <qex>demiss</qex>⟦br⟧
